            <h1 style="text-align: center;"><strong>Covid-19 Update Center:</strong></h1>

<hr>
<h2 style="text-align: center;">4/20/20: MiChild and Health Kids Insurance Program</h2>

<p style="text-align: center;">Take a look at the flyer below to get more information about these insurance programs, especially during difficult times and possible financial hardship. <br><a target="_blank" href="https://www.smore.com/tag19"><span class="text-label-primary">MiChild and Health Kids Insurance Program</span></a></p>

